                            </layoutDesc>
                </objectDesc>
            <handDesc hands="1">
              <handNote xml:id="handNote1" scope="sole" script="syr" medium="unknown">
                <desc>This manuscript is written in a good, regular hand of the <origDate
                    notBefore="1200" notAfter="1300">xiiith cent.</origDate></desc>
              </handNote>
            </handDesc>
            <decoDesc/>
            <additions>
              <p/>
              <list>
                <item n="1" xml:id="addition1">
                  <locus from="98a" to="98a"/>
                  <p>A note on fol. 98 a states that the manuscript was written by one
                      <persName>'Abdā</persName>, for the <persName>abbat Basil</persName>,
                      <persName>rabban Yuhannān</persName>, <persName>rabban Gabriel</persName>, and
                    the rest of the brotherhood; but the name of the convent is not mentioned,
                    though it was probably that of <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/360">S.
                      Mary Deipara</placeName>.</p>
                  <p>
                    <quote xml:lang="syr">ܐܬܟܬܒ ܟܘܪ̈ܣܐ ܗܠܝܢ ܐܘܟܝܬ ܛܟܣܐ ܕܥܠ ܢܨ̇ܝܚܐ ܩܕܝܫܐ ܡܪܝ ܒܪܨܘܡܐ
                      ܒܐܝ̈ܕܝ ܚܛܝܐ ܘܡܠܸܐ [ܡܘ]ܡ̈ܐ ܘܚܒܪ̈ܬܐ ܥܒܕܐ ܕܘܝܐ ܘܚܛܝܐ܀ ܒܝ̇ܨܝܦܘܬܐ ܕܪܒܢ ܒܐܣܝܠ
                      ܪܫܕ[ܝܪܐ] ܪܚ̇ܡ ܐܠܗܐ. ܘܪܒܢ ܝܘܚܢܢ ܘ . . . ܘܪܒܢ ܓܒܪܐܝܠ ܣܒܐ ܥ . . . ܐܚܘܬܐ ܩܕܝܫܬܐ
                      ܘܨܡܝܕܬ . . . ܩܕܝܫܐ. ܒܒܥܘ ܨ̇ܠܘ ܏ܘܫ</quote>
                  </p>
                </item>
              </list>
            </additions>
